#: .\effects_override.json
msgid "Chilly"
msgstr "微寒"

#. ~ Description of effect 'Chilly'.
#: .\effects_override.json
#, c-format
msgid "Your %s is exposed to the cold."
msgstr "你的%s暴露在寒冷中。"

#. ~ Speed name of effect(s) 'Chilly, Cold, Freezing'.
#: .\effects_override.json
msgid "Cold"
msgstr "寒冷"

#. ~ Description of effect 'Cold'.
#: .\effects_override.json
#, c-format
msgid "Your %s is very exposed to the cold."
msgstr "你的%s严重暴露在寒冷中。"

#: .\effects_override.json
msgid "Freezing"
msgstr "严寒"

#. ~ Description of effect 'Freezing'.
#: .\effects_override.json
#, c-format
msgid "Your %s is dangerously cold!"
msgstr "你的%s处于危险的寒冷状态！"

#: .\effects_override.json
msgid "Warm"
msgstr "温暖"

#. ~ Description of effect 'Warm'.
#: .\effects_override.json
#, c-format
msgid "Your %s feels warm."
msgstr "你的%s感到温暖。"

#. ~ Speed name of effect(s) 'Warm, Hot, Scorching'.
#: .\effects_override.json
msgid "Hot"
msgstr "炎热"

#. ~ Description of effect 'Hot'.
#: .\effects_override.json
#, c-format
msgid "Your %s is sweating from the heat.  Be careful not to get sick."
msgstr "你的%s因炎热而冒汗。小心别生病。"

#: .\effects_override.json
msgid "Scorching"
msgstr "酷热"

#. ~ Description of effect 'Scorching'.
#: .\effects_override.json
#, c-format
msgid "Your %s is sweating profusely!"
msgstr "你的%s大汗淋漓！"

#: .\modinfo.json
msgid "Temperature Effects Removed"
msgstr "温度效果移除"

#. ~ Description for Temperature Effects Removed
#: .\modinfo.json
msgid ""
"Removes temperature effects for your character. Never be hot or cold again! "
"Warning: if mod is loaded into current save/game your character status will "
"permanently display temperature state as of save though it has no effect on "
"your character."
msgstr ""
"移除角色所受的温度影响。从此不再感到炎热或寒冷！警告：若将模组载入当前存档/游戏，角色状态将永久显示存档时的温度状态，但这不会对角色产生实际影响。"
